# рҹӨ– Trading Bot вҖ” O'rnatish Yo'riqnomasi

## рҹ“Ғ Fayllar
```
trading_bot/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ main.py          # Asosiy bot
в”ңв”Җв”Җ ai_handler.py    # GPT-4 AI javoblar
в”ңв”Җв”Җ chart.py         # Grafik chizish
в”ңв”Җв”Җ market_data.py   # Narx va tahlil
в”ңв”Җв”Җ news.py          # Yangiliklar (RSS)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ requirements.txt
в””в”Җв”Җ .env.example
```

---

## вҡҷпёҸ O'rnatish

### 1. GitHub ga yuklang
```bash
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/username/trading-bot.git
git push -u origin main
```

### 2. Render.com sozlamalari
- **Build Command:** `pip install -r requirements.txt`
- **Start Command:** `python main.py`
- **Environment:** Python 3

### 3. Environment Variables (Render.com da)
| Key | Value |
|-----|-------|
| `TELEGRAM_TOKEN` | BotFather dan olingan token |
| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | OpenAI dan olingan kalit |

---

## рҹҡҖ Bot Buyruqlari

| Buyruq | Tavsif |
|--------|--------|
| `/start` | Botni ishga tushirish |
| `/narx BTCUSDT` | BTC narxini ko'rish |
| `/narx ETHUSDT` | ETH narxini ko'rish |
| `/narx XAUUSD` | Oltin narxini ko'rish |
| `/narx EURUSD` | EUR/USD narxini ko'rish |
| `/tahlil BTCUSDT` | Kuchli zonalar tahlili |
| `/grafik BTCUSDT` | Grafik + zonalar rasmi |
| `/yangilik` | So'nggi moliyaviy yangiliklar |

---

## рҹ“Ҡ Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan juftliklar
- `BTCUSDT` вҖ” Bitcoin
- `ETHUSDT` вҖ” Ethereum
- `XAUUSD` вҖ” Oltin
- `EURUSD` вҖ” Euro/Dollar
- `GBPUSD` вҖ” Funt/Dollar
- `USDJPY` вҖ” Dollar/Yapon Iyenasi